Earl Grey Chiffon Cake 🌿🥰
I learnt that failures bring you to a better place so don’t be afraid to fail, because you can learn from your mistakes! Here’s my chiffon cake recipe that I’ve came up with after a few rounds of testing - After you get the hang of this cake, trust me, you will start getting addicted to trying all kinds of flavors like me!! 😋😋😋 #ShersVideoRecipes
@serenetomato Yes!! I believe you can do it too 💯
@alexiaasim if you have more flour hahaha
